### Get All Accounts
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts?pageable.page=0&pageable.size=10
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Create Account
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "accountType": "SAVINGS",
  "currency": "USD",
  "nickname": "My Savings"
}

### Get Account
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/1
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Update Account
PATCH http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/1
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "Updated Savings"
}

### Close Account
DELETE http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/1
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Account Balance
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/1/balance
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Account Summary
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/1/summary
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Account Statement
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/1/statement?startDate=2023-01-01&endDate=2023-12-31
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Download Account Statement
POST http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/1/statement/download
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "startDate": "2023-01-01",
  "endDate": "2023-12-31",
  "format": "pdf"
}

### Freeze Account
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/1/freeze?reason=SuspiciousActivity
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Unfreeze Account
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/1/unfreeze
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Set Primary Account
PUT http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/1/primary
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Balance History
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/1/balance/history?startDate=2023-01-01&endDate=2023-12-31&pageable.page=0&pageable.size=10
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Account Types
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/types
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get All Accounts Summary
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/summary
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Get Account Statistics
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/statistics
Authorization: Bearer <access-token>

### Health Check
GET http://localhost:8080/api/v1/accounts/health
